results.title: Brighton "True Heart" Bracelet, Charm Link Bracelet, Chain, Live Love Laugh Dream, Silver and Gold, Adjustable, Collectible Preppy Boutique
results.description:
Brighton "True Heart" charm/chain bracelet in great condition. This bracelet is made up of four square charms; each is engraved "Live Laugh Love Dream" on a silver toned square. In the center of each square is a gold toned heart, and each square has a gold outer border. Each square charm is connected to the next charm by three rolo chains.

The bracelet closes with a lobster claw. From the last charm hangs Brighton's signature heart, engraved "B". There is a small chain at the end of the bracelet, making it adjustable. It is approx. 7 1/2" long at the longest length and 6 5/8" at the shortest length. From the end of this chain hangs a gold heart.

The back of each square charm is engraved with black hearts.

Each square charm measures approx. 5/8" x 1/2". There is approx. 1" of space between each square charm.

There are small signs of wear such as small scratches. However these are only visible under close observation, this piece will look brand new when you're wearing it. Priced accordingly.

This is the perfect addition to any Brighton lovers collection!
